modName: Catwoman Costume - CBBE - UNP - Works with 7B
summary: Adds a sexy Catwoman costume to Skyrim!
descriptionHtml:
[img]https://copy.com/HXv4kPnY0qtc[/img]


Hi there!

This mod adds a Catwoman costume to Skyrim. This costume is a part of one of my upcoming mods. 
I was working on my Batman mod (Woops, i spoiled it) when i realized that alot of people might want a Catwoman outfit for their, either female character, or follower *Cough* [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53005/?]Jessica[/url] *Cough*
-Just kidding, but please do check her out.

- Screenshots would be appreciated :)

[color=#339933][size=6][b]Location[/b][/size][/color]

Like the rest of my mods, there is a chest, to the right of The Bannered Mare in Whiterun.
Inside that chest the Catwoman costume should be, split up in 3 parts (Hat, Gloves, Torso)

[color=#ffcc33][size=5][b]Extra[/b][/size][/color]

This costume, aslo looks very much like Black Widows costume, so it could probably be used for that.

This costume also looks very good used with Sevenbase (infact it is what i use in the screenshots)
